### Arquivo para testar as rotas da API
### Use com Thunder Client, REST Client ou Postman

### 1. Registrar usuário
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "usuario@exemplo.com",
  "password": "123456",
  "username": "meuusername",
  "name": "Meu Nome Completo"
}

### 2. Login
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "usuario@exemplo.com",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 3. Registrar segundo usuário para testes
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "usuario2@exemplo.com",
  "password": "123456",
  "username": "usuario2",
  "name": "Segundo Usuário"
}

### ========================================
### ENDPOINTS DE PERFIL (REQUER AUTENTICAÇÃO)
### ========================================

### 4. Obter meu perfil
GET http://localhost:3000/profile/me
Authorization: Bearer SEU_TOKEN_AQUI

### 5. Atualizar meu perfil
PUT http://localhost:3000/profile/me
Authorization: Bearer SEU_TOKEN_AQUI
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Nome Atualizado",
  "bio": "Minha nova bio incrível!",
  "avatar": "https://exemplo.com/avatar.jpg"
}

### 6. Buscar perfil por username
GET http://localhost:3000/profile/meuusername
Authorization: Bearer SEU_TOKEN_AQUI

### 7. Buscar perfis (busca)
GET http://localhost:3000/profile/search?q=usuario&limit=5
Authorization: Bearer SEU_TOKEN_AQUI

### ========================================
### ENDPOINTS DE PLANOS DE TREINO (REQUER AUTENTICAÇÃO)
### ========================================

### 8. Criar novo plano de treino (ex: "ABC")
POST http://localhost:3000/workout-plans
Authorization: Bearer SEU_TOKEN_AQUI
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "ABC",
  "description": "Plano de treino dividido em 3 dias",
  "isPublic": true
}

### 9. Obter meus planos de treino
GET http://localhost:3000/workout-plans/me
Authorization: Bearer SEU_TOKEN_AQUI

### 10. Obter planos públicos
GET http://localhost:3000/workout-plans/public?limit=10

### 11. Buscar planos de treino
GET http://localhost:3000/workout-plans/search?q=ABC&limit=5&publicOnly=true

### 12. Obter plano específico por ID
GET http://localhost:3000/workout-plans/ID_DO_PLANO
Authorization: Bearer SEU_TOKEN_AQUI

### 13. Atualizar plano de treino
PUT http://localhost:3000/workout-plans/ID_DO_PLANO
Authorization: Bearer SEU_TOKEN_AQUI
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "ABC Atualizado",
  "description": "Descrição atualizada do plano",
  "isPublic": false
}

### 14. Deletar plano de treino
DELETE http://localhost:3000/workout-plans/ID_DO_PLANO
Authorization: Bearer SEU_TOKEN_AQUI

### ========================================
### ENDPOINTS DE DIAS DE TREINO (REQUER AUTENTICAÇÃO)
### ========================================

### 15. Adicionar dia ao plano (ex: Segunda = "A")
POST http://localhost:3000/workout-plans/ID_DO_PLANO/days
Authorization: Bearer SEU_TOKEN_AQUI
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "dayOfWeek": "monday",
  "workoutName": "A",
  "description": "Treino A - Peito, Ombro e Tríceps"
}

### 16. Obter dias do plano
GET http://localhost:3000/workout-plans/ID_DO_PLANO/days
Authorization: Bearer SEU_TOKEN_AQUI

### 17. Atualizar dia do treino
PUT http://localhost:3000/workout-days/ID_DO_DIA
Authorization: Bearer SEU_TOKEN_AQUI
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "workoutName": "A1",
  "description": "Treino A modificado"
}

### 18. Deletar dia do treino
DELETE http://localhost:3000/workout-days/ID_DO_DIA
Authorization: Bearer SEU_TOKEN_AQUI

### ========================================
### ENDPOINTS DE EXERCÍCIOS (REQUER AUTENTICAÇÃO)
### ========================================

### 19. Adicionar exercício ao dia de treino
POST http://localhost:3000/workout-days/ID_DO_DIA/exercises
Authorization: Bearer SEU_TOKEN_AQUI
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Supino Reto",
  "sets": 3,
  "repsRange": "8-12",
  "weight": 80,
  "restSeconds": 90,
  "order": 1,
  "notes": "Foco na técnica"
}

### 20. Obter exercícios do dia
GET http://localhost:3000/workout-days/ID_DO_DIA/exercises
Authorization: Bearer SEU_TOKEN_AQUI

### 21. Atualizar exercício
PUT http://localhost:3000/exercises/ID_DO_EXERCICIO
Authorization: Bearer SEU_TOKEN_AQUI
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Supino Inclinado",
  "sets": 4,
  "repsRange": "10-15",
  "weight": 70,
  "notes": "Banco a 30 graus"
}

### 22. Deletar exercício
DELETE http://localhost:3000/exercises/ID_DO_EXERCICIO
Authorization: Bearer SEU_TOKEN_AQUI

### ========================================
### COMANDOS CURL ALTERNATIVOS
### ========================================

### Registrar usuário via curl:
# curl -X POST http://localhost:3000/auth/register \
#   -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
#   -d '{"email":"test@test.com","password":"123456","username":"testuser","name":"Test User"}'

### Login via curl:
# curl -X POST http://localhost:3000/auth/login \
#   -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
#   -d '{"email":"test@test.com","password":"123456"}'

### Obter perfil via curl (substitua TOKEN):
# curl -X GET http://localhost:3000/profile/me \
#   -H "Authorization: Bearer SEU_TOKEN_AQUI"

### Atualizar perfil via curl:
# curl -X PUT http://localhost:3000/profile/me \
#   -H "Authorization: Bearer SEU_TOKEN_AQUI" \
#   -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
#   -d '{"name":"Novo Nome","bio":"Nova bio"}'

### Criar plano de treino via curl:
# curl -X POST http://localhost:3000/workout-plans \
#   -H "Authorization: Bearer SEU_TOKEN_AQUI" \
#   -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
#   -d '{"name":"ABC","description":"Plano de treino ABC","isPublic":true}'

### Obter meus planos via curl:
# curl -X GET http://localhost:3000/workout-plans/me \
#   -H "Authorization: Bearer SEU_TOKEN_AQUI"

### Adicionar dia ao plano via curl:
# curl -X POST http://localhost:3000/workout-plans/ID_DO_PLANO/days \
#   -H "Authorization: Bearer SEU_TOKEN_AQUI" \
#   -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
#   -d '{"dayOfWeek":"monday","workoutName":"A","description":"Treino A"}'